{"tid":1525971,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"9月1機場交通壓力測試實時討論","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:14:21.000Z","uid":204307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1ac4f437c6047d050d79ef697b705cbbd31b72","tid":1525971,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"1120 機場T1多狗 810開始見到大型水馬嚴格限制人流（巴士總站對住嘅門口check機票先入得）<br />\n930現場已經有不少網媒 記者採訪機場送機人士點樣入到黎<br />\n1000 T1 D、J企三隻狗<br />\n1100開始見到唔少狗拎住兩個頭盔入去T1；T2得警察報案中心有狗 及三架狗車泊係T2側門 其餘地方全部清淨無狗<br />\n圖為T1偏向A區狀況<br />\n1140離開機場向九龍方向非常順通<br />\n注意⚠️ 機場wifi由八點開始慢過之前令機場癱瘓嗰兩日 然後內裏人數不多 原因不明<br />\n支那遊客依然多：）<br />\n網好lag 上圖慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/whmruHz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwhmruHz.jpg&h=d6e54021&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k3xKgn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk3xKgn5.jpg&h=9170f07a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/742RFPW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F742RFPW.jpg&h=3ab0dd25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPYdUah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPYdUah.jpg&h=31e79a19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nP9kzaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnP9kzaw.jpg&h=ede15cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sj5jPJ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSj5jPJ5.jpg&h=3b0c3b86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFFvWpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFFvWpu.jpg&h=f69cd8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH2Nwv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH2Nwv.jpg&h=e7648f51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Z76uK7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Z76uK7.jpg&h=4f12b220&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qkSx9Lo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqkSx9Lo.jpg&h=616b53aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbcabc6966016386703f2a70909a0f5c0fcdd942","tid":1525971,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:48:06.000Z","msg":"9月1 測試機場交通！"},{"pid":"2989e9b25c5323daeee7b43ff858c67221ed3d71","tid":1525971,"uid":100046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"📣9月逢周末<br />\n機場交通壓力測試<br />\n✨頭炮 1/9 1300✨<br />\n<br />\n✅DO<br />\n揸車 (東涌、機場貨站+天雨車速）<br />\ncall 車<br />\n搭車<br />\n路面往返機場睇風景<br />\n見隊就排<br />\n<br />\n❌DON'T<br />\n入客運大樓<br />\n阻旅客<br />\n<br />\n貨車出唔到黎 貨運pk 就真揸春袋了😏<br />\n<br />\n#BeWATER #BeHUMBLE #BePOLITE"},{"pid":"a45cae7448f7f1fd94109b78f59c0d45a7ea1c9d","tid":1525971,"uid":689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef24df0c8261db05f9e8dfc665f9f07ea810271","tid":1525971,"uid":226974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"91a0669f5d92c3fc40ba3a65d3c927cfd7133521","tid":1525971,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8fed5b77454bb5f747b9dfb646d9bba291c73f8","tid":1525971,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:54:13.000Z","msg":"1140離開機場各A車都有人排隊 人次比較少 每架15人以下；E車每架10人內"},{"pid":"4842e06a964b167c741ef22e063f92958a9bc092","tid":1525971,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:55:49.000Z","msg":"強調 早上0745開始見到巴士總站正對面客運大樓門口 大概10個外聘人員 詳細檢查機票、送機人士"},{"pid":"45b4901dce2bcac3a2c83ca1f23755bcd5228d56","tid":1525971,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4842e06a964b167c741ef22e063f92958a9bc